<quote>當時忠義隻<measure quantity="10" unit="people">
<num value="10">百十</num>人</measure>
<pc>，</pc>其他軍皆南軍乘勢將帶<pc>，</pc>若潰將何以還<pc>？</pc>
</quote>
<pc>”</pc>
<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
<num value="1">一</num>人</measure>曰<pc>：</pc>
<pc>“</pc>
<quote>製司必欲追之<pc>，</pc>不若有官者棄官<pc>，</pc>無官者歸山東為<num value="100">百</num>姓<pc>。</pc>
